This paper discusses the use of AI as a service and the potential for misuse, which falls under the category of artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also explores the legal and technical challenges of monitoring for misuse, which could fall under the categories of cybersecurity (cs.CR), machine learning (cs.LG), cybercrime (cs.CY), and software engineering (cs.SE).
